features: 【Value Pack】You will get 2 pack value safety eyes set. There are about 748 pieces different sized safety eyes and noses and about 374 pieces different sized spacers in total. Sufficient quantity, various styles and rich colors make the plush dolls more beautiful and energetic, which can meet your diverse DIY decoration needs. It is a great decoration for DIY plush toys.

【Premium Material】These black safety eyes and noses are made of high quality plastic, it is smooth to the touch and Shiny, durable and not easy to damage, no fade. Since the safety eyes and nose are uniformly made by machine, there may be some blemishes, which you can gently scrape off with a tool. It does not affect your decoration effect.

【Multi-Sizes】There are 4 styles of crochet safety eyes, 9 sizes of pure black eyes ; black and white spot eyes has 3 sizes 2 styles，nose has three styles, 13mm pitted nose, 12mm oval eyes, pure color black nose has 3 sizes,There is also a large size 27mm black nose,22mm black eyes . You can also give the finished product as a gift to your children or friends, and they will be very surprised.

【Easy to Use】You need to pass the safety eye through the gasket ( the glitter eye needs to use the glitter gasket), then pass through the place you want to install, and finally fix it with a gasket, which plays a role in preventing the craft safety eye from falling off .Note: The eyes and gaskets of stuffed animals are small, parents should accompany the children when children under 6 years old are using it, so as not to eat by mistake.

【Wide Application】The safety eyes crochet accessories are the best accessories for all kinds of crafts, such as needle felt crafts, doll clothing buttons,teddy bears, plush toys, handmade projects and more. Crochet safety eyes can be used to DIY decorations and dolls with your family, and the finished product will add a cheerful atmosphere to your home.
